title: Dickies FR Long Sleeve Twill Shirt
description: DFL574: The Flame-Resistant Long Sleeve Twill Shirt by Dickies.  This durable relaxed fit, flame-resistant shirt has a generous fit across the shoulders to give you plenty of room for movement.  It’s constructed with a sturdy 7 oz twill cotton-nylon fabric blend that’s FR treated, has an ARC Rating of 8.6, is rated HRC (Hazard Risk Category) Category Level 2, and is both NFPA 70E and NFPA 2112 compliant.  This shirt also features a spread collar, two mitered chest pockets with button closures, and rounded cuffs with doghouse sleeve plackets.  Carefully designed and constructed for protection and comfort, this garment will stand up to tough working conditions.  Dickies, Quality Workwear since 1922.
